            "notes": "This deck focuses on using a combination of disruption spells and efficient creatures to control the board and pressure the opponent. It utilizes a mix of hand disruption spells like Inquisition of Kozilek, Hymn to Tourach, and Thoughtseize, along with removal spells like Fatal Push, Swords to Plowshares, and Vanishing Verse to disrupt the opponent's strategy. The deck also includes powerful creatures like Skyclave Apparition, Restoration Angel, and Solitude to apply pressure and provide additional disruption. With a mix of efficient removal and threats, this deck aims to disrupt the opponent's game plan while steadily building a board presence to close out the game quickly."
